
For Gnome 2:
  Put the .desktop file in /usr/share/applications/
  Put the .xpm files in /usr/share/pixmaps/

For Gnome:
  Copy directory file to /usr/share/gnome/apps/NPS_Utilities/.directory
  Put the .desktop file in /usr/share/gnome/apps/NPS_Utilities/
  Put the .xpm files in /usr/share/pixmaps/

For KDE 1.x:
  Copy directory file to /usr/share/applnk/NPS_Utilities/.directory
  Put the .desktop file in /usr/share/applnk/NPS_Utilities/
  Put the .xpm files in /usr/share/icons/ and /usr/share/icons/mini/

For KDE 2.x:
  Copy directory file to /usr/share/applnk/NPS_Utilities/.directory
  Put the .desktop file in /usr/share/applnk/NPS_Utilities/
  Put the .xpm files in /usr/share/icons/locolor,hicolor/16x16/apps/

